sequenceDiagram
    participant P as PacMan
    participant Pel as Pellet
    participant EB as EventBus
    participant SM as ScoreManager
    participant GM as GameManager
    participant G as Ghost

    Note over P,G: Power Pellet Eaten Sequence

    P->>Pel: OnCollision(IEntity)
    Pel->>EB: Publish(PowerPelletEaten, data)
    EB->>SM: Notify(PowerPelletEaten)
    SM->>SM: AddPoints(50)
    EB->>GM: Notify(PowerPelletEaten)
    GM->>G: SetState(Frightened)
    G->>G: Switch strategy to FrightenedStrategy
    Pel->>Pel: OnDestroy()
